data.description: ***** PRICE REDUCED $25,000 ****** Cute and Cozy 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with 22 solar panels. This home has an open kitchen with plenty of cabinets and counter space and tile flooring. The living room has a cozy brick fireplace, lots of windows to let the sun in, and hardwood floors. This home also features a laundry room with a counter, a hanger rack, tile flooring, and is equipped for either a gas or electric dryer. The large master bedroom has hardwood flooring and a ceiling fan. The remaining bedrooms also feature ceiling fans and hardwood floors.  The roof on the house and garage are less than a year old. The water heater is also new. The backyard is spacious and the patio has an aluminum cover. There’s also a 2 car detached garage. This home is close to shopping, the freeway, and local entertainment.
